column16: Rougned Odor flies out to left fielder Dayan Viciedo.
Adam Rosales singles on a line drive to center fielder Adam Eaton.   Jim Adduci scores.    Adrian Beltre to 2nd.
J.  P.   Arencibia pops out to first baseman Jose Abreu in foul territory.
Adrian Beltre walks.   Jim Adduci to 2nd.
Jim Adduci singles on a ground ball to shortstop Alexei Ramirez.
Elvis Andrus grounds out, second baseman Leury Garcia to first baseman Jose Abreu.
